headline.print_headline: Yanukovich Tried to Flee Ukraine: Parliamentary Speaker
headline.main: Yanukovich Tried to Flee Ukraine: Parliamentary Speaker

lead_paragraph: Ukraine's parliamentary speaker was quoted on Saturday as saying President Viktor Yanukovich had tried to board a plane to Russia but had been prevented from doing so and was now in the Donetsk region.
